Metadata.Title: Kill Order: 1-06-5346770-53
Metadata.Description: As a seasoned assassin, you have been entrusted with the most hardest assignment of your career. The client, whose identity remains undisclosed, requires the elimination of six high-value targets in the bustling city of Marrakesh. This clandestine operation, codenamed "Operation Mirage Fury," demands a combination of stealth, resourcefulness, and a willingness to operate beyond the boundaries of the law.
